The,UIDAI,s,mandate,is,to,issue,every,resident,a,unique,identification,number,linked,to,the,resident,s,demographic,and,biometric,information,which,they,can,use,to,identify,themselves,anywhere,in,India,and,to,access,a,host,of,benefits,and,service,The,UIDAI,proposes,to,provide,online,authentication,using,demographic,and,biometric,data,The,API,provides,authentication,services,to,residents,making,requests,for,government,agency,services,It,uses,RESTful,calls,and,responses,are,formatted,in,XML